; toolchange_gcode = ; Run custom tool change G-code\n{if current_extruder == next_extruder}; Check if tool is already active at startup\nT[current_extruder]; Tool already active, don't change tools\n{else}  ; Run tool change as expected\nM400    ; Wait for current moves to finish\nG60 S3  ; Save position to slot 3\nT-1     ; Drop off current tool\nM400    ; Wait for current moves to finish\nT[next_extruder]      ; Pick up next tool\n{if fan_always_on[next_extruder] == false}; If fan not set to always on, check if fan should run\n{if cooling[next_extruder] == false}; If auto cooling is off, set fan manually\n{if layer_z <= disable_fan_first_layers[next_extruder]}; check if fan should be on for first layers\nM106 S0 ; Set part cooling fan based on filament profile\n{else}; If layer height is above the minimum, enable fan\nM106 S{digits((min_fan_speed[next_extruder] * 0.01), 3, 2)} ; Set part cooling fan based on filament profile\n{endif}\n{endif}\n{endif}\nM116 P[current_extruder] ; wait for extruder to reach temp\nG1 R3 X0 Y0 Z2; Return to XY position saved in slot 3\nM400 ; Wait for previous move to finish\nG1 R3 X0 Y0 Z0; Return to position saved in slot 3\n{endif}
